snippet.title: The Conquest of Go - Early Access Trailer (Out on 12/7/2020)
snippet.description:
Get it at https://store.steampowered.com/app/12...
The Conquest of Go will be released for Steam Early Access on December 7, 2020. The game combines the gameplay of the classic board game Go (Igo, Baduk, Weiqi), with a unique campaign experience and online play.  View the full features list for the game on Steam at the link above.
Follow for future updates:
Twitter - https://twitter.com/WolfeyStudios
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/wolfeystudios/
